ShuffleBarrier.cpp- barrier class, similar to the given 
    example in resources, but adapted to have two different
    conditions, one for the zero thread, and another for
    the others
ShuffleBarrier.h- h for ShuffleBarrier
MapReduceFramework.cpp - implements the frameworks api
Utils.cpp- used for exit
